org.apache.jackrabbit.spi
Interface QueryInfo

public interface QueryInfo

QueryInfo is the the return value of RepositoryService.executeQuery(SessionInfo, String, String, Map) which is used to run a query on the RepositoryService. It provides access to the rows of the query result as well as to the column names.

See Also:
QueryResult.getRows(), QueryResult.getColumnNames(), QueryResult.getNodes()
